Package org.echo.mobile.framework.model.contract.output

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OutputValueType
    Describes functionality for contract result decoder
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountAddressOutputValueType
    Implementation of interface OutputValueType for account address types. Can decode addresses with account prefix "1.2." and without it.
    AddressOutputValueType
    Implementation of interface OutputValueType for all address types. Decodes prefixed address values. For example, account address: 1.2.1. If address is not clear, throws exception.
    BooleanOutputValueType
    Extension of class NumberOutputValueType for boolean type
    ContractAddressOutputValueType
    Implementation of interface OutputValueType for contract address types Can decode addresses with contract prefix "1.16." and without it.
    ContractOutputDecoder
    Decodes output contract data according to required output types
    EthContractAddressOutputValueType
    Implementation of interface OutputValueType for ethereum contract address types
    FixedArrayOutputValueType
    Implementation of interface OutputValueType for fixed arrays
    FixedBytesOutputValueType
    Implementation of interface OutputValueType for fixed bytes types types
    ListValueType
    Implementation of interface OutputValueType for list of one type
    NumberOutputValueType
    Implementation of interface OutputValueType for number types
    OutputValue
    Defines model for contract decoder outputs
    OutputValueTypesKt  
    StringOutputValueType
    Implementation of interface OutputValueType for string types
